data.title: What do US military veterans think of the resignation of Eric Shinseki as Secretary of Veterans Affairs?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 4): He is not the problem, but finally realized that he wasn't the solution either. 

GENERAL Shinseki was used to functional chain of command. SECRETARY Shinseki should have known better.
